只能用行動支付，但當地人很少用行動支付，加上車輛被人為破壞的比例高，以及釜山地形不平騎單車很費力，點出了諸多缺點。<br />\n<br />\n此外，在澳洲的留學生則指出，由於澳洲法律規定騎單車要帶頭盔，但一般人根本不可能隨身帶著頭盔去找ofo，加上城市人口少、地勢不平坦，主要是供大於求。<br />\n<br />\n對於ofo撤出海外多個國家的狀況，ofo並沒有給出回應。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/2610887\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F2610887&d=LW9BPaYju2cXFN7lLAFZbsn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=3cbcbd88\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F2610887&h=ebba5c0b\" target=\"_blank\">http://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/2610887</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T10:53:52.000Z","msg":"乜撚野撤退呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係回國再創業呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1ab3984ff64c5dbf9a1e745df7e7ad200e02d64","tid":900394,"uid":90464,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T11:07:27.000Z","msg":"攞哂信用卡bigdata同按金然後走佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1081a47bc31944d5a4f77e35456139565b903d35","tid":900394,"uid":47674,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"cfa2d7a2a63843f5ef866d715760f2f2e1663a6b","tid":900394,"uid":39365,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"f01f634eb7d4e2a9c6a7e5c9068c709ab3bbf4ae","tid":900394,"uid":164730,"like":94,"dislike":1,"score":93,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T08:56:03.000Z","msg":"明明只係用app租單車，點解啲新聞總係共享單車共享單車咁叫？<br />\n<br />\n咁我用foodpanda係咪共享餐廳？"},"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T09:13:48.000Z","msg":"因為好聽易接受囉, 共享係大陸幾平民, D人咩野都共享, 包括人妻"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T11:16:22.000Z","msg":"共產單車<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12cc996e6218e6d7a71086f072ea163ab37af14d","tid":900394,"uid":150609,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"ci